snippet.title: Dante’s Rant Room
snippet.description:
Hey guys! Thanks for stopping by, and I hope you guys enjoy my content! Drop a comment to start a conversation and I hope that I can earn your follow!

On this channel we talk about anime, movies, games (#teamxbox), and tv shows! If that's what you are into then this is the right channel for you!

Subscribe to be part of the conversation!
and win awesome giveaways!
Thanks for tuning into my channel!
